            Our mission is to empower businesses and individuals by providing innovative, easy-to-use tools that enhance productivity and growth.
        </p>
    </section>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer style="background: #1f2937; color: #fff; text-align: center; padding: 30px 20px; margin-top: 50px;">
        <p>&copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> MyApp. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
